### Route Implementation

#### [MODIFY] [auth.py](file:///d:/Projects/Antigravity/project%201/project%201.1/backend/app/routes/auth.py)
* Register the following path operations:
  * `POST /api/auth/register`: Takes `RegisterRequest`, returns `UserResponse`, maps duplicate errors to `409`, outputs `201 Created` status code.
  * `POST /api/auth/login`: Takes `LoginRequest`, returns `TokenResponse`, maps credentials errors to `401`, outputs `200 OK`.
  * `GET /api/auth/me`: Protected by `Depends(get_current_user)`. Returns `UserResponse` DTO for the currently active session.

